message.body: Hi jurgen. How are you today?
Alive. Not sure if I'm alert enough to manage the chunk of work that's in front of me right now. And you?
Coffee usually helps me when i feel like that. I'm doing great. I'm happy to be home and out of the rain.
I'm glad for you. Fourish is when I usually hit my afternoon slump. Sometimes I take a short nap, but today I just lay down for a few minutes. I thought
I'd be able to work, but for quite a while there I couldn't keep my mind focused. And coffee this late keeps me up at night.
